---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Ground Game Guidance - You Are Welcome Here">
  <div class="space-y-16">
    <section class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-8 py-12">
      <div class="text-center space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 via-orange-500 to-red-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          You Are Welcome Here
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-300 font-medium">
          You are not crazy. You are not alone. This is for you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-4 border-l-4 border-primary pl-6 bg-gray-900/30 p-6 rounded">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary">What is Ground Game Guidance?</h2>
      <div class="text-lg space-y-4 text-gray-200">
        <p>
          Look, this isn't some corporate wellness bullshit. This is for people who don't fit anywhere else. Real people dealing with real trauma. We talk straight, we dig deep, and we use whatever tools work - including AI. You're not broken. You're just done with fake leaders and surface-level nonsense.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-4 border-l-4 border-accent pl-6 bg-gray-900/30 p-6 rounded relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-accent">How We Lead</h2>
      <div class="text-lg space-y-4 text-gray-200">
        <p>
          Real leadership? It's not about being on top. It's about protecting the people who need it most. Leaders light the path and guard the vulnerable. The pack moves itself. We create safety and direction - that's it. Steven and Eric walk with you, not above you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-4 text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-red-950/20 to-orange-950/20 p-10 rounded-lg border border-primary/30">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary">This Platform Is For You</h2>
      <div class="text-lg space-y-4 text-gray-200">
        <p>
          Built for outsiders, misfits, and anyone betrayed by fake leaders. <br>
          Trauma-informed. Emotion-focused. Honest.
        </p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-6">
          This is not just a website.<br/>
          <span class="text-primary">This is a movement.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="space-y-8 py-12 bg-gray-900/20 p-8 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 via-orange-500 to-red-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Join The Community
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 p-8 rounded-lg border border-primary/30 space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">$29 Community Access</h3>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">$29<span class="text-lg text-gray-400">/month</span></p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">
            Join the community and access core resources
          </p>
          <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/9B6fZg74dcMTaAd1PhgjC04" class="block w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-orange-600 hover:from-red-700 hover:to-orange-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105 text-center">
            Join Now
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent/30 space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent">$79 Full Access To The Ground Game Community</h3>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">$79<span class="text-lg text-gray-400">/month</span></p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">
            Complete access to all community features, events, and direct guidance
          </p>
          <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/bJebJ088h0074bPeC3gjC05" class="block w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-orange-600 hover:from-red-700 hover:to-orange-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105 text-center">
            Join Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
